  "title": "📣Station Attendant (Islandwide /shift duties) 📣",
  "description": "<p><strong>🟥Working location: Islandwide</strong></p>\n<p><strong>🟥Shift duties: 7am - 3pm / 3pm - 11pm / 11pm - 7am (Must rotate shift)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>🟥Salary: $1,700 - $1,800</strong></p>\n<p><strong>🟥6 days work</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Duties:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assisted customers with fueling, payments, and basic service needs</li>\n  <li>Maintained station cleanliness and replenished store stock</li>\n  <li>Ensured safety compliance and provided friendly customer service</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirement</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>No experience required, training provided</li>\n  <li>Able to work shift duties, weekends &amp; PH</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No: 19C9611</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Reg No: R1433735 Teng Wei Mun (Celest)</p>",
